{"filter":false,"title":"solution-anatomy.1.php","tooltip":"/version-3.0/IoT.1/solution-anatomy.1.php","undoManager":{"mark":100,"position":100,"stack":[[{"start":{"row":134,"column":87},"end":{"row":134,"column":88},"action":"insert","lines":[" "],"id":305}],[{"start":{"row":7,"column":25},"end":{"row":7,"column":26},"action":"remove","lines":["-"],"id":306}],[{"start":{"row":7,"column":25},"end":{"row":7,"column":26},"action":"insert","lines":[" "],"id":307}],[{"start":{"row":60,"column":51},"end":{"row":60,"column":52},"action":"remove","lines":["-"],"id":308}],[{"start":{"row":60,"column":51},"end":{"row":60,"column":52},"action":"insert","lines":[" "],"id":309}],[{"start":{"row":53,"column":61},"end":{"row":53,"column":62},"action":"remove","lines":["-"],"id":310}],[{"start":{"row":53,"column":61},"end":{"row":53,"column":62},"action":"insert","lines":[" "],"id":311}],[{"start":{"row":81,"column":13},"end":{"row":130,"column":19},"action":"remove","lines":["<div class=\"row\">","                   <div class=\"col-sm-6\">","                    <div class=\"widget-content themed-background text-light-op\" style=\"background-color:#2368a0 !important;padding:10px 10px;\">","                    <strong><font color=\"#ffffff\"><center>Integration</center></font></strong>","                  </div>","                  <div class=\"widget box\">","                     <div class=\"widget-content\" style=\"padding:7px !important;background-color:#eee;border: 1px solid #eee; padding:3px;\" >","                              <p class=\"methodText\">","                                The IoT platform should provide a API gateway so that all the functionality that is provided by the platform could be utilized by consuming the API exposed through the Gateway. This will allow to create custom application for the specific business necessities. The platform should provide some custom connectors to push the data directly to the data lakes or different enterprise application using EAI Layer.","                                </p>","                       </div>","                  </div>","               </div>","                ","              <div class=\"col-sm-6\">","                    <div class=\"widget-content themed-background text-light-op\" style=\"background-color:#8c8c8c !important;padding:10px 10px;\">","                    <strong><font color=\"#ffffff\"><center>Messaging</center></font></strong>","                  </div>","                  <div class=\"widget box\">","                     <div class=\"widget-content\" style=\"padding:7px !important;background-color:#eee;border: 1px solid #eee; padding:3px;\" >","                            <p class=\"methodText\">The are different features that we think should be supported by IoT platform. Which are transforming a messaging, Routing the message to the right Entiti(s). The platform should support the application of rules and has the capability to perform when a rule condition is passed. The orchestration supports to be provided at a bare minimum level, Operations that can be performed in few millisecond should be permitted by the platform.</p>","                        </center></div>","                  </div>","               </div>","               </div>","               <div class=\"row\">","              ","               <div class=\"col-sm-6\">","                    <div class=\"widget-content themed-background text-light-op\" style=\"background-color:#00aae7;padding:10px 10px;\">","                    <strong><font color=\"#ffffff\"><center>Security</center></font></strong>","                  </div>","                  <div class=\"widget box\">","                     <div class=\"widget-content\" style=\"padding:8px !important;background-color:#eee;border: 1px solid #eee; padding:3px;\" >","                             <p class=\"methodText\">","                                One of the major aspect of the platform, We need to provide security at network layer, Different type of data encryptions, Authentication the entry that is interfacing the platform and having some sort of authorization policy in place that will help us identify, If the entity is authorized or not.","                             </p>","                       </div>","                  </div>","               </div>","                <div class=\"col-sm-6\">","                    <div class=\"widget-content themed-background text-light-op\" style=\"background-color:#ef4048 !important;padding:10px 10px;\">","                    <strong><font color=\"#ffffff\"><center>Analytics</center></font></strong>","                  </div>","                  <div class=\"widget box\">","                     <div class=\"widget-content\" style=\"padding:7px !important;background-color:#eee;border: 1px solid #eee; padding:3px;\" >","                            <p class=\"methodText\">The data that is following through the system demands some real time analytics to be supported by the platform. The analytics within the platform may not provide the historical day but should be able to provide last few days history (More the better)</p>","                        </center></div>","                  </div>","               </div>","             </div>"]},{"start":{"row":81,"column":13},"end":{"row":212,"column":10},"action":"insert","lines":["<div id=\"tabs\">","                        <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\" role=\"tablist\">","      <li class=\"active\">","          <a href=\"#home\" role=\"tab\" data-toggle=\"tab\">","          Implementation","          </a>","      </li>","      <li><a href=\"#profile\" role=\"tab\" data-toggle=\"tab\">","            Process Innovation","          </a>","      </li>","      <li>","          <a href=\"#messages\" role=\"tab\" data-toggle=\"tab\">","            SAP S/4HANA","</a>","      </li>","      <li>","          <a href=\"#settings\" role=\"tab\" data-toggle=\"tab\">","             SAP Hybris","","          </a>","      </li>